'''维吾尔人权项目'''（{{lang-en|Uyghur Human Rights Project}}，{{lang-ug|'''ئۇيغۇر كىشىلىك ھوقۇق قۇرۇلۇشى'''}}，缩写为UHRP）是一个[[非营利组织|非营利]]的研究机构，总部位于[[美国|美国]][[华盛顿哥伦比亚特区|华盛顿哥伦比亚特区]]，旨在促进[[维吾尔人|维吾尔人]]的[[人权|人权]]。其主要目标为通过研究导向，“促进[[维吾尔人|维吾尔人]]和其他人们的人权与民主”。由于在中国准确、及时地收集信息面临独特的挑战，该组织认为，除了广泛地关注人权的组织之外，特别的关注维吾尔族危机的组织也尤为重要。<ref name=about/>维吾尔人权项目还举办相关活动，如专家小组，讨论维吾尔人面临的危机。<ref>{{cite news |url= https://www.icij.org/investigations/china-cables/huge-uptick-in-chinese-propaganda-over-uighur-camps-report-finds/ |title= ‘Huge uptick’ in Chinese propaganda over Uighur camps, report finds |website= The International Consortium of Investigative Journalists |first= Carmen Molina |last= Acosta |date= July 30, 2020 |accessdate= March 29, 2021}}</ref>

== 历史 ==

维吾尔人权项目由[[维吾尔裔美国人协会|维吾尔裔美国人协会]]在2004年成立，拥有8名全职员工。<ref name=about/>项目资金来自于[[美国国家民主基金会|美国国家民主基金会]]，2016年起注册为非营利免税组织，组织类型为[[501(c)条款|501(C)]]。<ref>{{cite web |url= https://www.devex.com/organizations/uyghur-human-rights-project-uhrp-73203 |title= Uyghur Human Rights Project (UHRP) |website= Devex |date= 2021 |accessdate= 28 January 2021}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= https://www.ned.org/uyghur-human-rights-policy-act-builds-on-work-of-ned-grantees/ |title= Uyghur Human Rights Policy Act Builds on Work of NED Grantees |website= National Endowment for Democracy |date= 29 May 2020 |accessdate= 28 January 2021}}</ref>

乌麦尔·卡纳特自2018年起担任该组织执行董事，他曾担任过[[世界维吾尔代表大会|世界维吾尔代表大会]]的副主席。<ref>{{cite news |url= https://intellectinterviews.com/2020/09/omer-kanat-uyghur-genocide/ |title= Omer Kanat / Uyghur Genocide |date= September 29, 2020|first= Pelle |last= Axelsson	  |accessdate= March 29, 2021 |website= IntellectInterviews}}</ref>联合创始人[[努里·特克尔|努里·特克尔]]担任董事会主席，<ref>{{cite news |url= https://apnews.com/article/f882f882239b4d22e608b5bb55d0eff3 |title= Q&A: Nury Turkel on Uighurs and new religious freedom post |website= Associated Press |first= Elana |last= Schor |date= June 5, 2020 |accessdate= March 29, 2021}}</ref>他被[[美国众议院议长|美国众议院议长]][[南希·佩洛西|南希·佩洛西]]任命为[[美国国际宗教自由委员会|美国国际宗教自由委员会]]的专员（2019—2022）。<ref>{{cite news |url= https://www.rfa.org/english/news/uyghur/uscirf-05262020130709.html |title= US House Speaker Appoints Uyghur Attorney Nury Turkel to Panel on Religious Freedom |website= Radio Free Asia |date= May 26, 2020 |accessdate= March 29, 2021 |first1= Alim |last1= Seytoff |first2= Joshua |last2= Lipes}}</ref>

2020年9月，维吾尔人权项目与其他五十个组织和专家共同向[[联合国人权理事会|联合国人权理事会]]呼吁任命一个调查委员会，调查针对维吾尔人和其他突厥穆斯林暴行罪。<ref>{{cite news |url= https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/9/15/activists-want-un-to-probe-genocide-of-chinas-uighur-minority |title= Activists want UN to probe ‘genocide’ of China’s Uighur minority |website= Al Jazeera |date= September 15, 2020 |accessdate= March 29, 2021}}</ref>

== 报告 ==

维吾尔人权项目以英文、中文发布分析报告，以维护维吾尔人根据国际人权标准所享有的公民、政治、社会、文化和经济权利。<ref>{{cite news |url= https://www.nytimes.com/2020/07/23/fashion/uighur-forced-labor-cotton-fashion.html |title= Coalition Brings Pressure to End Forced Uighur Labor |first1= Elizabeth |last1= Paton |first2= Austin |last2= Ramzy |newspaper= The New York Times |date= 10 August 2020 |accessdate= 28 January 2021}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url= https://www.nytimes.com/2014/11/24/world/asia/prosecution-of-uighur-students-underscores-perils-of-chinese-clampdown.html |title= Prosecution of Uighur Students Underscores Perils of Chinese Clampdown |first= Andrew |last= Jacobs |date= 23 November 2014 |accessdate= 28 January 2021}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url= https://www.washingtonpost.com/religion/uighurs-reflect-on-2009-violence-that-set-off-chinese-crackdown/2020/07/10/03ce53ae-c246-11ea-9fdd-b7ac6b051dc8_story.html |title= Uighurs reflect on 2009 violence that set off Chinese crackdown |first= Aysha |last= Khan |newspaper= The Washington Post |date= 10 July 2020 |accessdate= 28 January 2021}}</ref>

2020年7月，该组织发布名为“世界上最幸福的穆斯林：虚假信息，宣传和维吾尔族危机”的报告，报告中分析了[[中国共产党|中国共产党]]的反叙事手法，以应对侵犯人权行为不断升级和对国际社会的警告。<ref>{{cite news |url= https://www.saveuighur.org/new-report-from-uhrp-the-happiest-muslims-in-the-world-disinformation-propaganda-and-the-uyghur-crisis-july-2020/ |title=New Report from UHRP —“The Happiest Muslims in the World”: Disinformation, Propaganda, and the Uyghur Crisis, July 2020 |date= August 5, 2020 |website= Save Uighur |publisher= Justice for All |accessdate= March 29, 2021}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url= https://www.licas.news/2020/07/31/media-warned-against-chinese-propaganda-on-plight-of-uyghurs/ |title= Media warned against Chinese ‘propaganda’ on plight of Uyghurs |website= LiCAS.news |date= July 31, 2020 |accessdate= March 29, 2021}}</ref>

UHRP发布关于中共维吾尔族人权各个方面政策的报告，包括文化权利，如《被摧残的喀什噶尔：强制重建、掠夺和监控下的维吾尔文化摇篮》<ref>{{cite news |url= https://www.rfa.org/english/news/uyghur/destruction-06052020164031.html |title= Kashgar’s Old City Destruction Emblematic of Beijing’s Cultural Campaign Against Uyghurs: Report |website= Radio Free Asia |first= Joshua |last= Lipes |date= June 5, 2020 |accessdate= March 29, 2021}}</ref>、《榨取文化资源：对维吾尔族文化遗产的剥削和形式化》。<ref>{{cite news |url= https://www.brookings.edu/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/FP_20200914_china_oppression_xinjiang_millward_peterson.pdf |format= PDF |title= China's System of Opression in Xinjang: How It Developed and How to Curb It |first1= James |last1= Millward |first2= Dahlia |last2= Peterson |website= The Brookings Institution |date= September 2020 |accessdate= March 29, 2021}}</ref>

